bye , bye miss american songbook a long long time ago i can still remember how my sister used to play his songs and in the 80s changed his style songs like love touch were so vile and forever young was on the charts too long but this whole series makes me shiver with each new horror it delivers bad and cheesy music it always makes me so sick i ca n't remember if i spewed when i heard him sing `` it had to be you '' but his integrity tore in two the day the music died